WelcomeSettings.WelcomeMessage:
Welcome, [USERS], to the Unofficial DeVry IT Discord! A community built by students to help foster educational and professional growth; please introduce yourself in the #welcome-page channel and join our main discussions in the #main-hub-general .

You can find your fellow classmates 1 of 2 ways.
1.) Utilize the `/join` command. It behaves almost like Google. Type in a class or course you're looking for and it'll display results via a dropdown menu
2.) Inform a moderator which classes you're in.

Thanks, and welcome to the Unofficial DeVry IT Discord!
